  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees.",
    "Season the chicken breast with salt and black pepper.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a skillet and cook the chicken until browned on both sides.",
    "Transfer the chicken to the oven and bake for 15 minutes or until cooked through.",
    "Toast the whole wheat bread until lightly browned.",
    "Spread a small amount of lemon juice on each slice of toast.",
    "Slice the cooked chicken into thin strips.",
    "Top each slice of toast with a chicken strip, some parsley, and some basil.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
